import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react' import axios from 'axios' import HomeButton from '../common/HomeButton/HomeButton' import Rating from '../common/Rating/Rating' import Header from './Main/Header' const Airline = (props) => { const [airline, setAirline] = useState({}) const [review, setReview] = useState({}) const [loaded, setLoaded] = useState(false) useEffect(() => { const slug = props.match.params.slug const url = `http://localhost:3000/api/v1/airlines/${slug}` axios.get(url) .then( resp => { setAirline(resp.data) setLoaded(true) }) .catch( resp => {}) }, [props.match.params.slug]) return (
{ loaded && <>
title
description
review-form
}
) } export default Airline
